uration=200ms` `Power2` 补位 |\n\n#### 接口设计\n\n```typescript\nexport interfa
ce UIToastConfig extends UIPositionConfig, Partial<UISizeConfig> {\n  message: s
tring;\n  type?: UINotificationType;\n  duration?: number;\n  icon?: string;\n  
